0</ins><br />\n【攪珠遊擊戰】攪珠系統 (公測版 v1.0) 上線喇!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1389090\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1389090</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<ins>2) 第一次攪珠</ins><br />\n【7.31攪珠結果】今日嘅攪珠結果係... (公測中)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1391078\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1391078</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<ins>3) 一班IT義士研發系統 v2.0 (網頁版+App版)</ins><br />\n【攪珠遊擊戰】攪珠系統 beta v2.0 (公測)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1393769\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1393769</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<ins>4) 第二次攪珠</ins><br />\n【8.1攪珠結果】今日嘅攪珠結果係...<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1394124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1394124</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<ins>5) 第三次攪珠</ins><br />\n【8.2攪珠結果】今日嘅攪珠結果係...<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1397072\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1397072</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<ins>6) 第四次攪珠</ins><br />\n【8.4攪珠結果】今日嘅攪珠結果係中區警署<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1405798\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1405798</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">③ 暫時成效</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n［突然］深水埗開始多人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1391424\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1391424</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/02/091355_0a2342b0feb408807891b41fc1b09452.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F02%2F091355_0a2342b0feb408807891b41fc1b09452.png&h=1b7a1167&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MSFb6FY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMSFb6FY.jpg&h=4257353b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(圖片轉載自於葵涌巴絲)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>④ 問題 </strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我認同有巴打認為咁嘅遊擊行動出師無名<br />\n但出師有名 = 經過宣傳 &ne; 遊擊<br />\n出師有名就冇辦法做到攻其不備<br />\n呢點方面歡迎討論<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果真係要講遊擊目的<br />\n① 令狗仔防守成本大增<br />\n② 早日令狗仔軍團崩潰<br />\n③ 達到be water嘅極致<br />\n④ 減少義士受傷被捕<br />\n</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"56f249629090d71e35702497700c801d6cffd5d1","tid":1413491,"uid":47222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T10:15:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"30eb433e4df9a6426d6380dd04774d0ff17ab8cf","tid":1413491,"uid":259321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T10:15:41.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins></ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"70d0f7f68b7d57c4cc9ffd9c8b89d2af449ad594","tid":1413491,"uid":38691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T10:16:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"783bd4dab5cb10dae51a7f94dab3d67d57af3db7","tid":1413491,"uid":259321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T10:16:22.000Z","msg":"全部人 加 今日嘅攪珠結果係... TG (Channel) &darr;&darr;&darr;<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/gaochu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fgaochu&d=gCXZhEDRu%2BJLwH3IwIcohilkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=afd33383\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/gaochu</a><br />\n<br />\n行動 加 攪珠遊擊戰 TG (Group)&darr;&darr;&darr;<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/MbhF5RCoa2bWnQDjB3zdBg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FMbhF5RCoa2bWnQDjB3zdBg&d=gCXZhEDRu%2BJLwH3IwIcohilkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=a54ccc3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_bla